          A Diploma course with the duration of three (3) years (six semesters).<br /> <br />

           ii) Environmental Health Technology (EHT)<br />
          HND Course with the duration of four (4) years. <br /> <br />

          iii) Environmental Health Technician (EVT) <br />
          A Diploma course with the duration of three (3) years.<br /><br />

          iv) Environmental Health  Assistant (EHA) <br />
            Certificate course with the duration of two (2) years.

        </p>

