       <h3>Mode of admission</h3>

       <p> 
        Various heads of departments are responsible for short-listing applicants of
        their departments for aptitude test, after which successful candidates are 
        expected to come along with original copies of their credentials, and go through
        an interview and screening processes. Candidates who are successful after 
        these processes are offered admission to run the programme which they chose. 
